%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20message%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20the%20common%20man.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aiming%20for%20jan-bhagidaari%20(people's%20participation)...%20It%20is%20our%20collective%20responsibility%2C%20this%20is%20the%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20take%20G20%20to%20the%20country%20and%20not%20confine%20it%20to%20conference%20halls%20and%20Delhi%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20common%20man%2C%20politics%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfaraway%20world%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20raise%20issues%20at%20the%20G20%20they%20can%20understand.%20It%20is%20also%20essential%20in%20view%20of%20the%20steps%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%2C%20the%20minister%20mentioned%20the%20Centre's%20drive%20to%20popularize%20millets%20as%20a%20staple.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20production%20of%20millet%20can%20be%20increased%2C%20you%20will%20increase%20nutrition%2C%20reduce%20climate%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20view%20of%20the%20expanding%20role%20of%20G20%2C%20the%20foreign%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20longer%20they%20put%20off%20reforms%2C%20the%20less%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20UN%20will%20be%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20G20%20is%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20UN%2C%20he%20indicated.%20%26quot%3BG20%20will%20pursue%20its%20mandate%2C%20UNSC%20will%20pursue%20its.%20One%20cannot%20be%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20other.%20Each%20has%20a%20place%20and%20its%20own%20contribution%2C%26quot%3Bhe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20is%20marked%20by%20over%20200%20events%20held%20across%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20the%20big%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Sept