0politics%20and%20his%20statement%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war%26quot%3B%20summed%20up%20global%20sentiment%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20that%20one%20sentence%2C%20which%20he%20said%20when%20he%20was%20meeting%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20Samarkand...%20In%20a%20way%2C%20if%20I%20were%20to%20take%20a%20single%20sentence%20of%20global%20sentiment...%20Global%20sentiment%20today%20does%20not%20envisage%20conflict%20or%20war%20as%20a%20solution%20because%20it%20has%20so%20many%20consequences%20for%20everybody's%20life.%20I%20would%20say%20he%2C%20in%20that%20one%20sentence%2C%20articulated%20what%20were%20the%20views%20of%20very%20diverse%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20described%20PM%20Modi%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20foreign%20policy.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BAnd%20not%20just%20now.%20I%20first%20met%20him%20in%202011%2C%20he%20was%20in%20China%20for%20a%20few%20days%20and%20I%20was%20the%20ambassador.%20I%20found%20him%20very%20interested%2C%20very%20insightful%20but%20very%20willing%20to%20learn%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20all%20of%20that.%20Since%20then%2C%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20I%20travel%20a%20lot%20with%20him.%20A%20lot%20of%20his%20travels%20are%20constantly%20trying%20to%20understand%20what's%20happening%20where%20and%20what's%20new.%20He%20is%20constantly%20looking%20at%20best%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693309260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fjem1lnh8_narendra-modi-vladimir-putin-ani-modi-putin-ani_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpms-not-an-era-of-war-comment-to-putin-summed-up-global-sentiment-s-jaishankar-4339395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM's%20%26quot%3BNot%20An%20Era%20Of%20War%26quot%3B%20Comment%20To%20Putin%20Summed%20Up%20Global%20Sentiment%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpms-not-an-era-of-war-comment-to-putin-summed-up-global-sentiment-s-jaishankar-4339395%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpms-not-an-era-of-war-comment-to-putin-summed-up-global-sentiment-s-jaishankar-4339395%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpms-not-an-era-of-war-comment-to-putin-summed-up-global-sentiment-s-jaishankar-4339395%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Supply%20Chains%20Disrupted%2C%20Whole%20World%20Suffers%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20issue%20facing%20the%20B20%20grouping%20is%20supply%20chain%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20showed%20how%20issues%20in%20supply%20chain%20can%20disrupt%20economies%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EB20%20is%20the%20official%20dialogue%20forum%20of%20G20%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20global%20business%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20issue%20before%20B20%20is%20the%20supply%20chain.%20Manufacturing%20is%20over-concentrated.%20The%20pandemic%20proved%20that%20a%20situation%20like%20this%20can%20disrupt%20economies%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20ways%20to%20democratise%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20and%20how%20to%20encourage%20green%20growth%20through%20sustainability.%20The%20minister%20added%20that%20it%20was%20critical%20to%20plug%20the%20gaps%20in%20investment%20flow%2C%20digital%20equity%20and%20gender%20issues.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20G20%20doesn't%20raise%20these%20issues%2C%20who%20will%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said%20the%20world%20will%20come%20to%20India%20%26quot%3Bbecause%C2%A0it%20has%20capacity%20and%20capability%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20there%20will%20be%20geopolitics%20in%20play.%20But%20it%20is%20important%20for%20us%20to%20find%20ways%20of%20growing%20manufacturing%20in%20this%20country.%20Because%20this%20is%20a%20pro-employment%20policy.%20There%20is%20a%20big%20opportunity%20for%20us%3A%20the%20world%20wants%20more%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20it%20wants%20to%20see%20transparency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3BChina%2B1%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20impact%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20on%20global%20supply%20chain%20had%20resulted%20in%20steep%20rise%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20eyeing%20solutions%20to%20its%20supply%20chain%20concerns%20caused%20by%20health%20crises%2C%20disasters%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20events.%20The%20coronavirus%20crisis%20and%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20are%20among%20the%20recent%20events%20that%20disrupted%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%2C%20resulting%20in%20steep%20price%20rises%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20India%20is%20pushing%20hard%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20hub%20and%20an%20alternative%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20B20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%20Sunday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20outlined%20India's%20role%20in%20building%20an%20efficient%20and%20trusted%20global%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20keynote%20address%20at%20the%20closing%20session%20of%20the%20Summit%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20recalled%20how%20India%20supplied%20vaccines%20beyond%20the%20borders%20and%20emerged%20as%20the%20'Pharmacy%20of%20the%20World'%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20world%20needed%20medicines%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20India%2C%20as%20the%20'Pharmacy%20of%20the%20World'%2C%20provided%20life-saving%20drugs%20to%20more%20than%20150%20countries.%20When%20the%20world%20needed%20a%20Covid%20drug%2C%20India%20enhanced%20production%20of%20its%20own%20vaccines%20to%20save%20the%20precious%20lives%20of%20millions%20across%20the%20globe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20pitched%20for%20a%20sustainable%20approach%20to%20business%20and%20said%20global%20businesses%20should%20understand%20that%20sustainability%20itself%20is%20an%20opportunity%20and%20a%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693309200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fa29dct7_jaishankar-ndtv-650_650x400_29_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-supply-chains-disrupted-whole-world-suffers-s-jaishankar-to-ndtv-4339461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20key%20issue%20facing%20the%20B20%20grouping%20is%20supply%20chain%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20showed%20how%20issues%20in%20supply%20chain%20can%20disrupt%20economies%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-supply-chains-disrupted-whole-world-suffers-s-jaishankar-to-ndtv-4339461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-supply-chains-disrupted-whole-world-suffers-s-jaishankar-to-ndtv-4339461%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-supply-chains-disrupted-whole-world-suffers-s-jaishankar-to-ndtv-4339461%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haley%20slams%20Ramaswamy's%20'childish%20name-calling'%22%2C%