ly%20changes%2C%20nothing%20will%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20agree%20that%20people%20who%20preach%2C%20don't%20practice%20it.%20What%20we%20have%20to%20do%20is%2C%20with%20our%20actions%2C%20we%20have%20to%20show%20the%20world.%20We%20must%20debate%20at%20the%20debating%20forums.%20But%20we%20have%20to%20embarrass%20people%20if%20they%20back%20out%20of%20promises%20made%20(at%20talk%20shops).%20As%20a%20voice%20of%20The%20Global%20South%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20gone%20to%20125%20countries%20and%20asked%20them%20about%20G20%20issues.%20The%20climate%20issue%20is%20getting%20worse.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20different%20department.%20Climate%20disasters%20are%20happening%20regularly%20and%20have%20become%20a%20major%20economic%20disruptor.%20If%20supply%20chains%20are%20interrupted%20by%20climate%20changes%2C%20your%20entire%20economy%20will%20be%20in%20jeopardy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Global%20South%20knows%20they%20are%20the%20Global%20South.%20Because%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Global%20South%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20development%2C%20income%2C%20and%20history%2C%20and%20is%20a%20place%20in%20the%20heart.%20Anyone%20can%20say%20we%20are%20the%20Global%20South.%20But%20do%20you%20behave%20that%20way%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Global%20South%20are%20those%20who%2C%20whatever%20their%20limited%20resources%2C%20will%20do%20for%20other%20countries%20because%20we%20feel%20we%20all%20are%20a%20part%20of%20a%20family%20and%20their%20problem%20is%20our%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20tour%20countries%2C%20I%20notice%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20countries%20have%20started%20speaking%20to%20us%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20When%20they%20see%20the%20efficiency%20and%20scale%20of%20our%20schemes%2C%20they%20see%20these%20as%20inspiration%20and%20feel%20this%20can%20be%20replicated%20and%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20an%20example%3B%20we%20give%20motivation%20and%20solidarity%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0a%20new%20method%20of%20solving%20old%20problems.%20Our%20delivery%20is%20commensurate%20with%20the%20developed%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20put%20out%20such%20maps%20in%20the%20past%20where%20they%20have%20claimed%20territories%20that%20don't%20belong%20to%20them.%20Putting%20out%20a%20map%20does%20not%20mean%20anything.%20These%20territories%20are%20very%20much%20a%20part%20of%20India.%20We%20are%20very%20clear%20what%20our%20territories%20are.%20Making%20absurd%20claims%20does%20not%20make%20other%20people's%20territories%20yours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693307760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fiq2cqi_jaishankar_650x400_29_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexternal-affairs-minister-dr-s-jaishankars-interview-to-ndtv-top-quotes-4339313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20wide-ranging%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-In-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20outlined%20India's%20position%20in%20world%20order%2C%20its%20role%20in%20addressing%20global%20challenges%20and%20how%20it%20has%20emerged%20as%20voice%20of%20Global%20South%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexternal-affairs-minister-dr-s-jaishankars-interview-to-ndtv-top-quotes-4339313%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexternal-affairs-minister-dr-s-jaishankars-interview-to-ndtv-top-quotes-4339313%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexternal-affairs-minister-dr-s-jaishankars-interview-to-ndtv-top-quotes-4339313%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for