s%2010%20student%20because%20he%20wrote%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20class%20blackboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher%20and%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%20were%20both%20also%20suspended.%20The%20government%20has%20ordered%C2%A0two%20separate%20enquiries%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20registered%20by%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20juvenile%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20son%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%2010%2C%20was%20beaten%20severely%20by%20the%20teacher%20and%20principal%20of%20the%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20at%20Bani%20for%20writing%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogan%20on%20blackboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20said%20in%20the%20complaint%20that%20at%20around%20noon%20on%20August%2025%20(Friday)%20when%20teacher%20Farooq%20Ahmad%20entered%20the%20classroom%2C%20he%20found%20that%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20was%20written%20on%20the%20blackboard.%20He%20then%2C%20allegedly%2C%20beat%20the%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20claimed%20that%20Ahmad%20then%20then%20took%20the%20minor%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20principal%20and%20that%20he%20was%20beaten%20up%20there%20by%20Ahmad%20and%20principal%20Muhammad%20Hafeez.%20The%20room%20was%20locked%20during%20the%20beating%2C%20the%20complaint%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20juvenile%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20treatment%2C%20it%20further%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomeone%20called%20me%20over%20the%20phone%20on%20August%2025%20and%20told%20me%20that%20my%20son%20has%20been%20thrashed%20in%20the%20school.%20I%20immediately%20left%20home%20and%20trekked%20on%20foot%20to%20reach%20his%20rented%20accommodation.%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20him%20writhing%20in%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20father%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20triggered%20protests%20by%20students%20on%20August%2026.%20Several%20local%20leaders%20also%20visited%20the%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20sections%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20342%20(wrongful%20confinement)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20the%20duo%20at%20the%20Bani%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20section%2075%20of%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202015%2C%20have%20also%20been%20added%20to%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStation%20House%20Officer%20of%20the%20Bani%20Police%20Station%2C%20Arjun%20Magotra%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20arrested%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20of%20school%20education%20department%20have%20placed%20Farooq%20Ahmad%20and%20Muhammad%20Hafeez%20under%20suspension%20and%20ordered%20an%20enquiry%20by%20Director%20of%20School%20Education%20at%20Jammu%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20for%20suspension%20by%20the%20department%20was%20issued%20on%20August%2026%2C%20the%20day%20when%20the%20family%20of%20the%20boy%20registered%20a%20complaint%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20administration%20of%20Kathua%20has%20also%20ordered%20a%20separate%20enquiry%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Kathua%20has%20constituted%20a%20three-member%20committee%20comprising%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%2C%20deputy%20chief%20education%20officer%20Kathua%20(Billawar)%20and%20Principal%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kharote%2C%20to%20enquire%20into%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20submit%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20along%20with%20specific%20comments%20and%20recommendations%20for%20proceeding%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20apart%20from%20fixing%20the%20responsibility%20against%20the%20culprit(s)%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20former%20CM%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20said%20that%20hate-mongers%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20spare%20kids%20and%20appreciated%20police%20for%20prompt%20action%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHate%20mongers%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20spare%20kids%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20venomous%20mindset.%20Appreciate%20the%20prompt%20action%20taken%20by%20Kathua%20police%20in%20filing%20an%20FIR.%20Odd%20that%20in%20the%20UP%20case%2C%20police%20is%20pressurising%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20father%20to%20drop%20charges%20against%20the%20teacher%20who%20encouraged%20students%20to%20thrash%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CUP%20case%E2%80%9D%20that%20Mufti%20is%20referring%20to%20came%20to%20light%20when%20a%20video%20showing%20the%20principal%20of%20a%20school%20forcing%20students%20to%20hit%20their%20Muslim%20classmate%20for%20not%20having%20learnt%20maths%20tables%20went%20viral.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20on%20how%20this%20student%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%5C%22%3Epushed%20to%20strike%20a%20compromise.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693305952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29161240%2FScreenshot-2023-08-29-at-4.09.27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjammu-kashmir-teacher-arrested-beating-student%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teacher%20and%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%20have%20both%20been%20suspended.%