ation%20and%20a%20severe%20real-estate%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jwilkins%40insider.com%20(Joseph%20Wilkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-slowdown-gdp-economists-targets-deflation-property-crisis-outlook-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20Article%20370%20Be%20Used%20To%20Scrap%20Itself%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20Big%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20the%20Centre%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Btimeframe%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20a%20state%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20while%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20against%20the%20repeal%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Brestoration%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20made%20the%20observation%20after%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20-%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20the%20move%20to%20bifurcate%20the%20state%20into%20union%20territories%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20measure%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20its%20statehood%20will%20be%20restored%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20asked%20if%20Article%20370%20can%20be%20used%20to%20amend%20Article%20370%20itself.%20%26quot%3BArticle%20370%20can%20be%20used%20to%20amend%20other%20provisions%20but%20can%20it%20be%20used%20to%20amend%20Article%20370%20itself%20%3F%20That's%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20sought%20to%20know%20that%20how%20the%20provision%20could%20be%20revoked%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20constituent%20assembly.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20Article%20367%20was%20amended%20through%20Article%20370%20with%20the%20concurrence%20of%20the%20state%20(J%26amp%3BK)%2C%20the%20petitioners%20wouldn't%20have%20challenged%20its%20scrapping%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20a%20due%20process%20was%20followed%20while%20abrogating%20the%20provision.%20%26quot%3BAs%20there%20was%20no%20council%20of%20ministers%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20then%2C%20the%20Governor%20exercised%20those%20powers.%20The%20President%20used%20Article%20370%20with%20the%20concurrence%20of%20Governor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20any%20change%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20%26quot%3Bbrings%20everyone%20at%20par%20can%20never%20be%20faulted%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20who%20were%20behind%20integration%20of%20the%20state%20with%20Union%20of%20India.%20The%20removal%20of%20some%20provisions%20could%20also%20be%20in%20furtherance%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%20-%20fraternity%2C%20equality-%20it's%20a%20basic%20structure%2C%20it's%20a%20part%20of%20brotherhood%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mehta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20opposing%20the%20repeal%20of%20Article%20370%20have%20been%20insisting%20that%20the%20provision%20could%20not%20have%20been%20abrogated%2C%20as%20the%20term%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20whose%20concurrence%20was%20required%20before%20taking%20such%20a%20step%2C%20ended%20in%201957%2C%20after%20it%20had%20drafted%20the%20erstwhile%20state's%20Constitution.%20With%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20having%20become%20extinct%2C%20Article%20370%20acquired%20a%20permanent%20status%2C%20they%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20agreement%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20earlier%20contended%20that%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bconstitutional%20fraud%26quot%3B%20in%20abrogation%20of%20the%20provision.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20wrong-doing%20and%20there%20was%20no%20constitutional%20fraud%20as%20alleged%20by%20the%20other%20side.%20The%20step%20was%20necessary%20to%20be%20taken.%20Their%20argument%20is%20flawed%20and%20inconceivable%2C%26quot%3B%20Attorney%20General%20R%20Venkataramanisaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693303620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchange-that-brings-everyone-at-par-centre-on-article-370-repeal-4338902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20the%20Centre%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Btimeframe%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20a%20state%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchange-that-brings-everyone-at-par-centre-on-article-370-repeal-4338902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchange-that-brings-everyone-at-par-centre-on-article-370-repeal-4338902%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchange-that-brings-everyone-at-par-centre-on-article-370-repeal-4338902%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20wild%20life%20of%20billionaire%20Twitter%20co-founder%20Jack%20Dorsey%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20eccentricities%20like%20eating%20one%20meal%20a%20day%2C%20and%20taking%20ice%20baths%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222745%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20Dorsey%20appears%20at%20a%20bitcoin%20convention%20on%20June%204%2C%202021%20in%20Miami%2C%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f938ad0729770012b936a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222058%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJack%20Dorsey%20has%20led%20an%20interesting%20life.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJack%20Dorsey%20%