l%2C%20and%20numerous%20properties%20with%20her%20mom%20and%20uncle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDouglass%20said%20she'd%20sought%20stronger%20connection%20with%20friends%20through%20these%20experiences%2C%20adding%20that%20homebuying%20should%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bsuperficially%20limited%26quot%3B%20to%20just%20significant%20others.%20Not%20all%20friends%20make%20good%20real-estate%20partners%2C%20Douglass%20said%2C%20but%20she's%20found%20that%20the%20complicated%20conversations%20she's%20had%20with%20friends%20over%20purchasing%20homes%20have%20paid%20off%2C%20as%20she%20was%20able%20to%20buy%20homes%20in%20desirable%20areas%20much%20sooner%20than%20most%20of%20her%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20say%20that%20that's%20a%20risk%20and%20you're%20going%20to%20lose%20that%20friend%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20treat%20you%20poorly%20or%20they're%20going%20to%20do%20you%20wrong.%20Or%20you%20can%20say%20this%20is%20going%20to%20make%20us%20closer%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20really%20get%20to%20know%20this%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Douglass%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20become%20a%20better%20person%20through%20partnering%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20my%20family%2C%20and%20you%20really%20learn%20about%20a%20lot%20about%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspecially%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Austin%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-housing-market-prices-surging-multi-unit-zoning-could-decrease-2023-7%5C%22%3Ebecome%20one%20of%20the%20least%20affordable%20US%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20partly%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-explained-mortgage-rates-fed-inventory-home-prices-house-2023-6%5C%22%3Esteep%20housing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Douglass%20said%20this%20method%20of%20homebuying%20could%20be%20a%20strategic%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuying%20homes%20with%20friends%20as%20investments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EModares%20and%20Douglass%20said%20teaming%20up%20with%20friends%20got%20them%20started%20on%20homebuying%20significantly%20faster%20than%20either%20thought%20was%20possible%2C%20especially%20when%20Modares%20said%20she%20didn't%20have%20a%20stable%20W-2.%20Closing%20on%20homes%20was%20much%20cheaper%20with%20friends%2C%20they%20said%2C%20and%20having%20shared%20responsibilities%20and%20workloads%20that%20could%20be%20divided%20efficiently%20was%20also%20a%20plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDouglass%20said%20Open%20House%20Austin's%20objective%20was%20%26quot%3Bto%20open%20people's%20minds%20away%20from%20just%20the%20traditional%20model%20of%2C%20I%20have%20to%20get%20married%2C%20and%20then%20before%20we%20have%20a%20kid%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20and%20move%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Modares%20and%20Douglass%20have%20had%20clients%20purchase%20homes%20with%20friends%20and%20then%20move%20in%20together%2C%20they%20said%20they'd%20encouraged%20some%20clients%20to%20buy%20homes%20with%20friends%20to%20use%20as%20investment%20properties%20that%20double%20as%20vacation%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20want%20to%20open%20people's%20minds%20up%20because%20when%20they%20think%20of%20buying%20with%20friends%2C%20they%20think%20everyone's%20living%20in%20the%20property%20together%2C%20but%20that%20sounds%20like%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Modares%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20not%20only%20buy%20the%20house%20with%20friends%2C%20renovate%20the%20property%20together%2C%20and%20then%20live%20in%20the%20property%20together%2C%20that%20would%20be%20a%20really%20good%20reality-TV%20show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20critical%20part%20of%20homebuying%20with%20friends%2C%20they%20said%2C%20is%20the%20operating%20agreement%2C%20which%20outlines%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20a%20real-estate%20partnership.%20The%20partnership%20will%20work%20only%20if%20everyone%20is%20on%20the%20same%20page%20about%20ownership%20percentage%2C%20initial%20cash%20contribut