%20and%20it%20can%20get%20brutal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20makes%20you%20so%20tired.%20I'd%20get%20off%20work%20and%20just%20go%20to%20sleep.%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20energy%20to%20do%20anything%20else%20during%20the%20workday%20and%20then%20I%20spent%20the%20weekend%20trying%20to%20recover%20to%20get%20ready%20for%20the%20upcoming%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20we're%20given%20a%20heat%20safety%20training%2C%20we%20end%20up%20having%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20each%20other%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.ups.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Four-company%2Fgreat-employer%2F5-ways-ups-is-improving-heat-safety-for-employees.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Egiven%20a%20heat%20training%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20we%20sign%20and%20never%20see%20again%20until%20next%20year.%20UPS%20also%20ordered%20more%20ice%20machines%20for%20our%20hubs%2C%20but%20those%20haven't%20been%20installed%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20watch%20each%20other%20for%20signs%20of%20danger.%20If%20managers%20notice%20someone%20reacting%20badly%20to%20the%20heat%2C%20they'll%20either%20send%20them%20home%20or%20bring%20them%20into%20an%20air-conditioned%20office%20to%20hydrate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20like%20my%20job%20well%20enough%20and%20make%20pretty%20good%20money%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20usually%20mind%20going%20to%20work.%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20overtime%2C%20which%20boosts%20my%20paycheck.%20My%20job%20is%20one%20of%20the%20physically%20easier%20ones%20in%20my%20warehouse%2C%20but%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-drivers-reveal-struggle-working-without-air-conditioning-heat-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Egoing%20into%20work%20during%20the%20summer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20just%20awful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20started%20to%20dread%20it.%20I've%20taken%20coworkers%20off%20the%20warehouse%20floor%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20one%20of%20the%20air-conditioned%20offices%20to%20let%20them%20rest%20and%20give%20them%20water%20to%20rehydrate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20don't%20understand%20what%20we%20as%20delivery%20workers%20go%20through%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20get%20really%20frustrated.%20I'll%20hear%20someone%20being%20mad%20that%20their%20package%20is%20late%20and%20it's%20like%2C%20dude%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20have%20that%20in%20one%20day.%20But%20we've%20gotten%20to%20this%20consumer%20mentality%20where%20we're%20used%20to%20clicking%20a%20button%20and%20having%20the%20product%20show%20up%20almost%20immediately%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20driven%20down%20the%20standards%20in%20the%20logistics%20industry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEverybody's%20trying%20to%20get%20packages%20out%20faster%20and%20cheaper%20%E2%80%94%20and%20faster%20and%20cheaper%20is%20almost%20always%20going%20to%20be%20more%20dangerous.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20A%20UPS%20spokesperson%20sent%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20Insider%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThe%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20every%20UPSer%20is%20our%20top%20priority.%20We%20have%20been%20steadily%20building%20on%20our%20efforts%20to%20protect%20our%20people%20in%20the%20face%20of%20increasingly%20hot%20temperatures%2C%20provide%20a%20safe%20work%20environment%2C%20and%20make%20working%20at%20UPS%20a%20great%20experience%20for%20employees%20as%20they%20serve%20our%20customers%20and%20strengthen%20our%20communities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20with%20top%20experts%20in%20heat%20safety%20to%20study%20our%20working%20conditions%20and%20further%20improve%20our%20trainings%20and%20protocols%20to%20help%20our%20employees%20work%20safely%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20on%20hot%20days.%20Improvements%20include%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EProviding%20and%20encouraging%20our%20employees%20to%20take%20appropriate%20breaks%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EA%20focus%20on%20how%20to%20prevent%20heat%20stress%20from%20occurring%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFollowing%20guidance%20from%20our%20heat%20experts%2C%20we're%20increasing%20access%20to%20ice%2C%20cool%20water%2C%20and%20electrolyte%20beverages%20in%20our%20facilities%20to%20ensure%20all%20UPSers%20have%20what%20they%20need%20to%20stay%20hydrated.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EInstalling%20additional%20fans%20at%20facilities%20across%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20the%20launch%20of%20our%20Recharge%20heat%20safety%20program%2C%20we're%20equipping%20our%20delivery%20drivers%20with%20new%20cooling%20sleeves%20and%20hats%20%E2%80%94%20developed%20in%20partnership%20with%20MISSION%C2%AE%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20athletic%20innovations%20off%20the%20playing%20field%20and%20court%20and%20into%20our%20operations%20in%20support%20of%20our%20industrial%20athletes.%20Studies%20show%20that%20cooling%20key%20parts%20of%20the%20body%20can%20help%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20overheating%2C%20and%20MISSION%C2%AE's%20state-of-the-art%20technology%20helps%20its%20cooling%20fabrics%20stay%20up%20to%2030%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20body%20temperature.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BRecharge%20is%20informed%20by%20sports%20science%20research%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Connecticut's%20Korey%20Stringer%20Institute%20and%20the%20Gatorade%20Sports%20Science%20Institute.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20have%20partnered%20with%20MISSION%2C%20a%20performance%20apparel%20company%20that%20is%20helping%20us%20to%20apply%20their%20knowledge%20developed%20in%20support%20of%20professional%20athletes%20to%20inform%20how%20we%20take%20care%20of%20our%20UPS%20industrial%20athletes.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BUPS%20and%20the%20Teamsters%20have%20also%20reached%20a%20tentative%20new%20agreement%20on%20heat%20safety%20with%20the%20Teamsters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20UPS%20driver%20with%20an%20interesting%20story%3F%20Contact%20Manseen%20Logan%20at%20mlogan%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-warehouse-jobs-summer-heat-package-handler-experience-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693300862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dfbe83bd98a60019798996%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-warehouse-jobs-summer-heat-package-handler-experience-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UPS%20warehouse%20jobs%20are%20awful%20and%20dangerous%20in%20the%20summer%20heat%2C%20a%20worker%20says.%20They%20wish%20customers%20considered%20package%20handlers'%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Fortesa%20Latifi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-warehouse-jobs-summer-heat-package-handler-experience-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tech%20stocks%20will%20start%20rallyin