e%20condemned%20the%20conduct%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20schoolteacher%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20who%20asked%20her%20seven-year-old%20students%20to%20beat%20a%20classmate%20who%20did%20not%20learn%20his%20multiplication%20tables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20that%20has%20since%20gone%20viral%2C%20Tyagi%20is%20also%20heard%20referring%20to%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20editorials%20below%20express%20concern%20about%20Tyagi%20making%20prejudicial%20comments%20inside%20a%20classroom.%20Many%20endorse%20exemplary%20punishment%20for%20her%2C%20and%20some%20juxtapose%20the%20situation%20%E2%80%98on%20the%20ground%E2%80%99%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20historic%20Moon%20landing%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Too%20much%20is%20at%20stake%E2%80%99%3A%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20editorial%20board%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com.%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Feditorials%2Fexpress-view-on-muzaffarnagar-video-teaching-hate-8913770%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20finds%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20incident%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20pattern%20of%20polarisation%3A%20%E2%80%9CAdmittedly%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20set%20in%20a%20larger%20backdrop.%20An%20increasing%20political%20polarisation%20is%20steadily%20trickling%20into%20public%20and%20private%20spaces%2C%20giving%20electoral%20contests%20a%20new%20edge%2C%20and%20circumscribing%20debates%20in%20between%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continues%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prejudice%20that%20made%20the%20teacher%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20choreograph%20the%20horrific%20punishment%20and%20draft%20seven-year-olds%20into%20its%20brutish%20design%2C%20and%20the%20normalisation%20of%20prejudice%20which%20dictates%20her%20and-so-what%20responses%20in%20the%20aftermath%2C%20speak%20of%20disquieting%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fnot-ashamed-up-teacher-justifies-slap-classmate-shocker-720277%5C%22%3ETyagi%20later%20downplaying%20the%20incident%20in%20media%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIE%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Esays%20that%20although%20civil%20society%20must%20take%20responsibility%20for%20countering%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20brutalisation%20of%20the%20classroom%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20is%20up%20to%20the%20political%20class%20to%20send%20an%20appropriate%20message%20following%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20too%20much%20at%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20editorial%20concludes%20by%20saying.%20%E2%80%9CQuite%20simply%2C%20the%20steps%20forward%20taken%20by%20the%20new%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20promote%20a%20more%20innovative%20teaching%20and%20a%20more%20creative%20learning%20%E2%80%A6%20will%20be%20tested%20if%20hate%20is%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20classroom%20%E2%80%93%20and%20get%20away%20with%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20separate%20incident%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kathua%20town%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1054954%2Fj-k-principal-teacher-booked-for-thrashing-student-who-wrote-jai-shri-ram-on-school-board%5C%22%3Ewhere%20a%20Muslim%20teacher%20beat%20a%20student%20for%20writing%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20blackboard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3Edoes%20not%20cancel%20out%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20outrage%20%E2%80%93%20it%20only%20adds%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Time%20for%20society%20to%20wake%20up%E2%80%99%3A%20the%20%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ffreepressjournal.in%2Fanalysis%2Fclassrooms-of-hate-amidst-lunar-triumph%5C%22%3Ean%20editorial%20by%20the%20Mumbai-based%20%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20says%20that%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20incident%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20normalisation%20of%20prejudice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20normalisation%20of%20this%20toxicity%2C%20be%20it%20in%20Manipur%2C%20in%20Haryana%20and%20now%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20is%20bound%20to%20have%20disastrous%20consequences%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EFPJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20warns.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EWhen%20school%20teachers%20become%20purveyors%20of%20hate%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20society%20as%20a%20whole%20to%20wake%20up%20and%20take%20action.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparing%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20and%20Kathua%20incidents%2C%20%3Cem%3EFPJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%20the%20different%20treatment%20given%20to%20the%20two%20offending%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20a%20teacher%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kathua%20district%20was%20promptly%20arrested%2C%20and%20rightfully%20so%2C%20for%20beating%20up%20a%20boy%20who%20wrote%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20class%20blackboard%2C%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20teacher%20is%20still%20freely%20giving%20interviews%20to%20the%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20incident%20taking%20place%20just%20a%20day%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFPJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20asks%20what%20kind%20of%20example%20the%20former%20has%20set.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EIs%20this%20what%20we%20want%20future%20generations%20in%20India%20to%20learn%3F%20Not%20the%20wonders%20of%20science%20and%20education%20but%20the%20narrow%20schisms%20of%20religion%20and%20%5Bbigotry%3F%5D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20editorial%20board%20concludes%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20incident%20has%20occurred%20just%20days%20before%20various%20world%20leaders%20are%20scheduled%20to%20arrive%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20when%20India%20will%20host%20a%20plethora%20of%20world%20leaders%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20is%20this%20the%20face%20of%20the%20country%20that%20the%20government%20wishes%20to%20project%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20capital%20is%20being%20spruced%20up%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-violence-g20-summit-and-delhi-dog-relocations%5C%22%3Eall%20unsightly%20elements%20are%20being%20swept%20away%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Can%20the%20bigotry%20and%20hatred%20also%20be%20cast%20aside%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fg20-cities-forced-evictions-beautification%5C%22%3ENo%20Mercy%20for%20the%20Vulnerable%20as%20Authorities%20Beautified%20Urban%20Areas%20for%20G20%20Events%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Teach%20the%20teacher%E2%80%99%3A%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20title%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fblogs%2Ftoi-editorials%2Fteach-the-teacher%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20editorial%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20the%20paper%20spotlights%20the%20discrimination%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20education%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20research%20going%20back%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fpapers%2Fw15057%5C%22%3E(Hanna%20and%20Linden%202009)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20discrimination%20towards%20minority%20students%20was%20noted%20among%20teachers%20in%20a%20medium-sized%20Indian%20city%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20investigation%20also%20found%20that%20much%20of%20the%20discrimination%20came%20from%20minority%20teachers%20themselves%2C%20which%20suggested%20that%20minority%20teachers%20may%20be%20internalising%20particular%20beliefs%20about%20their%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continues%20to%20say%20that%20these%20%E2%80%9Care%20not%20abstract%20academic%20concerns%20%E2%80%A6%20caste%20prejudice%20plays%20out%20even%20in%20elite%20institutions%20like%20%5Bthe%5D%20IITs.%20Making%20an%20example%20out%20of%20teacher-offenders%20like%20the%20one%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20is%20a%20good%20start%20to%20tackling%20this%20toxicity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20teacher%20is%20still%20making%20statements%20and%20not%20in%20custody.%20Do%20you%20need%20any%20more%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20evidence%20to%20take%20preliminary%20police%20action%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Downright%20macabre%E2%80%99%3A%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20editorial%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fet-editorial%2Fsay-repeat-hitting-children-is-wrong%2Farticleshow%2F103110320.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSay%20%26amp%3B%20repeat%3A%20Hitting%20children%20is%20wrong%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20condemns%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20to%20the%20media%20that%20she%20asked%20her%20students%20to%20beat%20their%20Muslim%20classmate%20owing%20to%20her%20inability%20to%20physically%20get%20up%20and%20beat%20the%20student%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTyagi%E2%80%99s%20explanation%20for%20fomenting%20this%20proto-lynch%20mob%20mentality%20inside%20a%20classroom%20%E2%80%93%20that%20she%20is%20differently%20abled%2C%20and%20so%20had%20to%20direct%20others%20to%20do%20the%20needful%20%E2%80%93%20is%20downright%20macabre%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Poison%20Has%20Now%20Reached%20India%E2%80%99s%20Schools%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHitting%20children%20is%20wrong.%20These%20four%20words%20need%20to%20be%20spelt%20out%20since%20not%20every%20law-abiding%20citizen%20in%20circa%202023%20India%20seems%20to%20think%20it%20applies%20to%20them%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20adults%20in%20positions%20of%20power%20and%20responsibility%20over%20young%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCorporal%20punishment%2C%20like%20ragging%2C%20must%20be%20recognised%20as%20crime%2C%20and%20not%20tolerated%20as%20part%20of%20some%20perverted%20notion%20of%20%E2%80%98tough%20love%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EET%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Econcludes%20its%20editorial%20by%20saying%20that%20while%20various%20laws%20exist%20to%20punish%20the%20physical%20abuse%20of%20children%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20(figurative)%20whip%20must%20come%20down%20on%20perpetrators.%20Adding%20a%20communal%20layer%20to%20violence%20against%20children%20makes%20the%20offence%20more%20grotesque.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Scar%20he%20has%20to%20live%20with%20forever%E2%80%99%3A%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShifting%20focus%20to%20the%20Muslim%20student%E2%80%99s%20plight%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnewindianexpress.com%2Fopinions%2Feditorials%2F2023%2Faug%2F28%2Fup-slapgate-poisoning-classes-with-communal-comments-corporal-punishment-2609273.html%5C%22%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ewrites%20in%20its%20editorial%20that%20his%20%E2%80%9Chumiliation%20%3Cspan%3Eis%20a%20scar%20he%20has%20to%20live%20with%20forever.%20The%20boy%20needs%20proper%20counselling%20to%20process%20and%20overcome%20the%20demeaning%20and%20dehumanising%20assault.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20condemning%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20statements%20after%20the%20fact%2C%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%20that%20she%20seemed%20to%20be%20unaware%20of%20her%20responsibilities%20as%20a%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20after%20the%20incident%20led%20to%20national%20outrage%2C%20the%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20comments%20suggest%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%20anything%20wrong%20in%20the%20punishment%20per%20se%20but%20only%20in%20its%20mode%20of%20delivery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20appeared%20unaware%20that%20corporal%20punishment%20was%20declared%20illegal%20by%20the%20Right%20of%20Children%20to%20Free%20and%20Compulsory%20Education%20Act%2C%202009.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchools%20should%20be%20safe%20places%20for%20students%20to%20grow%20and%20learn%2C%20not%20horror%20chambers%20for%20the%20persecuted%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20editorial%20ends%20by%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwide-range-of-fears-new-indias-muslims-have%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20Feeling%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20slap%20on%20communal%20harmony%E2%80%99%3A%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdeccanchronicle.com%2Fopinion%2Fdc-comment%2F270823%2Fdc-edit-a-slap-on-communal-harmony.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20editorial%3C%2Fa%3E%20draws%20our%20attention%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20choices%20the%20Muslim%20student%E2%80%99s%20father%20perceived%20as%20having%20after%20his%20son%20was%20beaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20the%20father%20of%20the%20child%20had%20first%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20teacher%2C%20indicating%20his%20total%20distrust%20in%20government%20machinery.%20%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20only%20after%20social%20and%20political%20organisations%20took%20up%20the%20matter%20that%20he%20lodged%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDC%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20writes%20about%20how%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20symptom%20of%20the%20neglect%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20education%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20teacher%20remaining%20unapologetic%20about%20her%20crude%20and%20inhuman%20method%20of%20teaching%20is%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20a%20pointer%20towards%20the%20scant%20attention%20we%20pay%20to%20our%20education%20system%20when%20we%20are%20supposed%20to%20invest%20in%20its%20qualitative%20and%20quantitative%20improvement%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20editorial%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%2C%20decades%20ago%2C%20set%20a%20target%20of%20earmarking%206%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20for%20education%20but%20the%20highest%20allocation%20as%20per%20the%20finance%20minister%20was%20made%20only%20this%20year%20at%204.5%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Islamophobia%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20classroom%E2%80%99%3A%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20editorial%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Feditorials%2Fdeepening-divide-538905%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CDeepening%20Divide%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%20that%20similar%20other%20incidents%20have%20preceded%20the%20one%20in%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20Islamophobia%20is%20becoming%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20classroom%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20increasing%20frequency%20of%20such%20cases%20being%20reported.%20Last%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fvideo-manipal-institute-of-technology-kasab-muslim-student-teacher%5C%22%3Ethe%20video%20clip%20of%20a%20Muslim%20student%20of%20Manipal%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Karnataka%20confronting%20his%20teacher%20for%20comparing%20him%20with%20Ajmal%20Kasab%20had%20gone%20viral%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20atmosphere%20of%20political%20polarisation%2C%20educational%20institutes%20should%20set%20an%20example%20by%20preaching%20and%20practising%20communal%20harmony.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20our%20country%20would%20be%20in%20danger%20of%20becoming%20tattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continues%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20endorsed%20punishment%20for%20Tyagi.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20found%20guilty%20of%20inciting%20hatred%2C%20the%20teacher%20should%20be%20given%20exemplary%20punishment%20that%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20all%20those%20who%20look%20at%20people%20through%20a%20communal%20prism%2C%20especially%20those%20belonging%20to%20the%20disadvantaged%20or%20minority%20sections%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693299589000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29142358%2FTripta-Tyagi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fenglish-newspaper-editorials-condemn-tripta-tyagis-conduct%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripta%20Tyagi%20was%20filmed%20asking%20her%20students%20to%20beat%20their%20Muslim%20classmate%20for%20not%20learning%20maths%20tables.%20Many%20editorials%20endorsed%20exemplary%20punishment%20for%20Tyagi%20given%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fenglish-newspaper-editorials-condemn-tripta-tyagis-conduct%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Toronto%20Film%20%E2%80%98Not%20a%20Word%E2%80%99%20Debuts%20Trailer%2C%20Director%20Hanna%20Slak%20Talks%20Truth%20of%20Mahler%E2%80%99s%205th%20Symphony%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20Have%20to%20Face%20the%20Darkness%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693299384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNo