%20%E2%80%9Cbunglings%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(NCSC)%2C%20Parmar%20%E2%80%93%20a%201992%20AGMUT%20cadre%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20accuses%20Sinha%20and%20Mehta%20of%20%E2%80%9Charassment%2C%20humiliation%2C%20intimidation%2C%20atrocious%20behaviour%20and%20frequent%20transfers%20for%20his%20being%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20solely%20for%20the%20reason%20that%20he%20blew%20%5Bthe%5D%20whistle%20and%20highlighted%20bunglings%20in%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20plans%20to%20provide%20every%20rural%20household%20with%20tap%20water%20by%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20is%20currently%20posted%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Public%20Enterprises%20and%20was%20principal%20secretary%20of%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20Department%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20May%202022%2C%20during%20which%20time%20he%20said%20he%20intimated%20the%20LG%2C%20chief%20secretary%20and%20other%20authorities%20about%20the%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cdismal%20status%20of%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20being%20implemented%20without%20doing%20SWOT%20(Strengths%2C%20Weaknesses%2C%20Opportunities%20and%20Threats)%20Analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20JJM%20works%20were%20progressing%20slowly%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20of%20erroneous%20and%20faulty%20procedure%20for%20allotment%20of%20works%E2%80%9D%20and%20misinterpretation%20of%20a%20clause%20of%20the%20Manual%20of%20Procurement%20of%20Works%2C%202019%20that%20one%20contractor%20can%20be%20awarded%20only%20two%20works%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Findia%2Fjk-dalit-ias-officer-files-complaint-of-harassment-humiliation-against-l-g-chief-secretary-1503216550.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Statesman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Parmar%20claims%20that%20LG%20Sinha%20on%20June%206%2C%202022%20threw%20him%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20room%20with%20the%20objective%20to%20%E2%80%9Charass%20and%20humiliate%20him%20without%20any%20fault%20and%20this%20was%20done%20in%20front%20of%20all%20the%20administrative%20secretaries%20of%20UT%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%20on%20July%2025%2C%202023%20also%20%E2%80%9Chumiliated%20and%20threw%20him%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20Committee%20of%20Secretaries%20without%20any%20fault%E2%80%9D.%20Parmar%20said%20he%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfrequent%20transfers%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20transfer%20policy%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20to%20the%20NCSC%20says%20that%20this%20process%20of%20%E2%80%9Cintimidation%20and%20harassment%20was%20done%20purposely%20due%20to%20prejudice%20and%20bias%20against%20him%20for%20being%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20his%20act%20of%20highlighting%20bunglings%20in%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20said%20he%20has%20apprehensions%20that%20LG%20Sinha%20chief%20secretary%20Mehta%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20damage%20his%20reputation%20and%20career%20by%20implicating%20him%20in%20false%20cases%20as%20he%20had%20pointed%20out%20many%20financial%20irregularities%20and%20acts%20of%20omission%20and%20commission%20of%20Mehta%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20RR%20Bhatnagar%20Advisor%20to%20LG%20and%20others%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Statesman%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20said%20he%20has%20also%20informed%20the%C2%A0Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%20about%20J%26amp%3BK%20officers%20providing%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%2C%20concocted%2C%20misleading%20and%20factually%20incorrect%20figures%20regarding%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693293651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F26190346%2FScreen-Shot-2021-04-26-at-7.03.28-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-ias-dalit-lg-manoj-sinha-harassment-humiliation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%20claimed%20in%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20that%20he%20was%20harassed%20and%20frequently%20transferred%20because%20he%20highlighted%20%E2%80%9Cbunglings%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-ias-dalit-lg-manoj-sinha-harassment-humiliation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chevron%3A%20Workers%20at%20major%20Australia%20gas%20facilities%20to%20strike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693292747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F373E%2Fproduction%2F_130924141_wheatstone-lng-first-cargo-departs-for-japan-d.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66643277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Industrial%20action%20at%20two%20plants%20raises%20concerns%20that%20energy%20prices%20could%20rise%20in%20Europe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A110%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66643277%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66643277.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66643277.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fandango%20Launches%20Sales%20on%20Cuba-Set%20Venice%20Days%20Opener%20%E2%80%98Oceans%20Are%20