%2F25184020%2FIMG_0015.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20no%20place%20for%20the%20minorities.%20I%20fear%20for%20the%20future%20of%20a%20country%20that%20has%20declared%20war%20against%20a%20section%20of%20its%20people.%20I%20fear%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Republic%20as%20our%20founding%20fathers%20had%20conceived%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20shared%20my%20misgivings%20with%20a%20dear%20friend%2C%20his%20glib%20response%20was%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20loses%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20the%20cowardly%20saffron%20hordes%20will%20fade%20away%20into%20the%20woodwork%20and%20our%20bustling%2C%20chaotic%20democracy%20will%20once%20again%20reassert%20itself.%20The%20mistake%20he%20makes%20is%20in%20presuming%20that%20the%20colossal%20damage%20done%20to%20institutions%20and%20the%20social%20fabric%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20stems%20purely%20from%20politics%20and%20will%20be%20mended%20once%20the%20authoritarian%20ruler%20and%20his%20minions%20are%20booted%20out%2C%20bag%20and%20baggage%2C%20the%20way%20the%20dictator%20and%20her%20hoodlums%20were%20after%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20my%20simple-minded%20buddy%20has%20ignored%20is%20that%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20there%20has%20been%20a%20frontal%20assault%20on%20our%20culture%2C%20of%20which%20politics%20is%20only%20one%20component.%20This%20regime%20%E2%80%95%20a%20gravedigger%20of%20culture%2C%20no%20less%20%E2%80%95%20has%20consciously%20divided%20us%20on%20religious%20lines%20and%20attacked%20lifestyles%2C%20traditions%2C%20art%2C%20learning%2C%20our%20collective%20memory%2C%20even%20how%20we%20love%20one%20another.%20It%20has%20devastated%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20a%20multicultural%20ethos%20based%20on%20liberal%20humanism%20that%20our%20founding%20fathers%20had%20conceived%2C%20and%20which%20was%20hitherto%20a%20stop-start%20work%20in%20progress.%20The%20damage%20inflicted%20seems%20irreparable.%20But%20I%20am%20getting%20ahead%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20generation%20of%20midnight%E2%80%99s%20children%20grew%20up%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%20willed%20ourselves%20to%20celebrate%20our%20common%20nationhood.%20%E2%80%98Unity%20in%20diversity%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20hopeful%20shibboleth%20by%20which%20we%20defined%20our%20priceless%20heritage%20of%20religions%2C%20languages%2C%20ethnicities.%20%E2%80%9CAmar%2C%20Akbar%2C%20Antony%E2%80%9D%20were%20catchwords%20that%20represented%20our%20collective%20aspiration%20for%20brotherhood%20by%20setting%20aside%20our%20differences.%20Our%20founding%20fathers%20spun%20the%20enchanting%20myth%20that%20we%20are%20a%20tolerant%2C%20non-violent%20people%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%2C%20although%20blood-soaked%20at%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20birth%2C%20we%20would%20endeavour%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20Nehruvian%20idea%20of%20a%20modern%2C%20inclusive%20democracy%20of%20religious%20tolerance%20and%20cultural%20pluralism.%20That%20ideal%20lies%20in%20tatters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20road%20to%20freedom%20was%20besmirched%20by%20unspeakable%20inhumanity%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20border%20as%20man%20killed%20man%20in%20a%20crazed%20religious%20frenzy.%20In%20lieu%20of%20gas%20chambers%20but%20equally%20productive%2C%20ordinary%20citizens%20brandishing%20swords%2C%20butchers%E2%80%99%20knives%2C%20guns%20and%20even%20their%20bare%20hands%2C%20went%20on%20a%20killing%20spree%20in%20a%20collective%20state%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthoughtlessness%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20term%20used%20by%20Hannah%20Arendt%20to%20describe%20the%20irrationality%20of%20the%20unspeakable%20evil%20committed%20by%20the%20Nazis.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20up%20to%202%20million%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20were%20butchered%20and%2020%20million%20people%20displaced%20in%20the%20holocaust%20of%20Partition.%20And%20there%20was%20no%20retribution%20for%20such%20evil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Solzhenitsyn%20had%20observed%20with%20devastating%20prescience%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20we%20neither%20punish%20nor%20reproach%20evildoers%2C%20we%20are%20ripping%20the%20foundations%20of%20justice%20from%20future%20generations.%E2%80%9D%20While%20the%20Nazis%20were%20hunted%20down%20and%20made%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20crimes%2C%20the%20millions%20of%20killers%20and%20their%20abettors%20during%20Partition%20quietly%20returned%20as%20anonymous%20lawful%20citizens%20of%20the%20two%20newly%20independent%20nations.%20It%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20infer%20that%20these%20criminals%20slipped%20back%20to%20their%20everyday%20roles%20as%20teachers%2C%20workers%2C%20maulvis%2C%20sadhus%2C%20government%20employees%20and%20what%20have%20you%3B%20but%20by%20letting%20these%20murderous%20vectors%20of%20hate%20go%20scot-free%20without%20even%20so%20much%20as%20a%20condemnation%20of%20their%20bestiality%2C%20there%20has%20been%20neither%20repentance%20nor%20redemptive%20change.%20(Is%20it%20any%20surprise%20that%20this%20regime%20that%20has%20fattened%20on%20hatred%2C%20has%20declared%20August%2014th%20as%20Partition%20Horrors%20Remembrance%20Day%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20alive%20the%20fratricidal%20bitterness%3F%20With%20like%20intent%2C%20the%20film%20Kashmir%20Files%20that%20spews%20venom%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%20has%20been%20bestowed%20the%20Nargis%20Dutt%20Award%20for%20Best%20Film%20on%20National%20Integration%20at%20the%2069th%20National%20Film%20Awards.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20miasma%20of%20distrust%20and%20hate%20engendered%20by%20Partition%20suppurated%20in%20these%20diseased%20souls%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20ready%20to%20strike%20when%20the%20time%20was%20ripe.%20The%20Partition%20savagery%20provided%20the%20template%20for%20the%20mass%20killings%20in%20Delhi%20in%201984%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201992-93%2C%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202002%20and%20myriads%20of%20lesser%20conflagrations.%20In%20no%20other%20country%20on%20earth%20have%20civilians%20killed%20their%20fellow%20beings%20in%20such%20monstrous%20numbers%20and%20with%20such%20frequency.%20We%20are%20undoubtedly%20among%20the%20cruellest%20people%20on%20earth!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20the%20religious%20bigotry%20plaguing%20this%20country%20were%20planted%20a%20century%20ago.%20As%20far%20back%20as%201921%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20at%20its%20very%20inception%20pronounced%20that%20that%20Hindus%20need%20a%20separate%20nation%20and%20Muslims%20must%20be%20denied%20any%20rights%20in%20it.%20This%20fuzzy%20notion%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20was%20formalised%20by%20VD%20Savarkar%20as%20an%20exclusivist%20and%20homogenising%20doctrine%20called%20Hindutva%20that%20is%20underpinned%20by%20an%20obsessive%2C%20visceral%20hatred%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F15155952%2Fhindu-mahasbha.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20photo%20of%20Hindu%20Mahasabha.%20Standing%20-%20Shankar%20Kistaiya%2C%20Gopal%20Godse%2C%20Madanlal%20Pahwa%2C%20Digambar%20Badge.%20Seated%20-%20Narayan%20Apte%2C%20Vinayak%20D.%20Savarkar%2C%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20Vishnu%20Karkare.%20Credit%3A%20Flickr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-163350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGroup%20photo%20of%20Hindu%20Mahasabha.%20Standing%20%E2%80%93%20Shankar%20Kistaiya%2C%20Gopal%20Godse%2C%20Madanlal%20Pahwa%2C%20Digambar%20Badge.%20Seated%20%E2%80%93%20Narayan%20Apte%2C%20Vinayak%20D.%20Savarkar%2C%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20Vishnu%20Karkare.%20Credit%3A%20Flickr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20behind%20the%20benign%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20nurturing%20Bharatiya%20culture%2C%20ethnocentric%20Hindutva%20has%20spread%20across%20the%20land%20through%20the%20furtive%20but%20relentless%20RSS%20machinery.%20Millions%20of%20young%20and%20old%20in%20Shishu%20Mandirs%2C%20Vidya%20Bharati%20schools%20and%20the%20ubiquitous%20shakhas%20across%20the%20country%20have%20been%20tutored%20in%20a%20hyper-nationalism%20that%20fosters%20an%20implacable%20hatred%20of%20Muslims%20who%20must%20pay%20for%20historical%20wrongs%20committed%20against%20Hindus.%20Even%20the%20Amar%20Chitra%20Katha%20comic%20series%20are%20exploited%20for%20propaganda%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%E2%80%9D%20conditioning%20of%20minds%20in%20what%20Sumit%20Sarkar%20terms%20%E2%80%9Ca%20Gramscian%20process%20of%20building%20up%20hegemony%20through%20molecular%20permeation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20brigade%20has%20succeeded%20in%20capturing%20the%20collective%20consciousness%20of%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Hindus%20and%20indoctrinating%20them%20in%20the%20gospel%20of%20Hindutva.%20A%20study%20across%20four%20states%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20in%202019%20showed%20that%2072%25%20of%20Indians%20had%20clear%20majoritarian%20views%20on%20issues%20relating%20to%20banning%20beef%2C%20religious%20conversions%2C%20love%20jihad%20etc.%20Since%20then%2C%20their%20numbers%20could%20only%20have%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20see%20today%20is%20Hindutva%20with%20a%20swagger.%20In%20January%20this%20year%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20the%20reigning%20pontiff%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20publicly%20enunciated%20the%20Hindutva%20doctrine%20with%20staggering%20bluntness.%20In%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20hate%20speech%2C%20he%20brazenly%20stated%20that%20Hindu%20society%20had%20finally%20awakened%20after%20being%20at%20war%20for%20over%201%2C000%20years%20and%20is%20now%20ready%20to%20do%20battle%20to%20defend%20Hindu%20society%2C%20Hindu%20Dharma%20and%20Hindu%20culture%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20against%20an%20enemy%20without%20but%20against%20an%20enemy%20within.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20he%20warned%20Muslims%20to%20%E2%80%9Cabandon%20their%20boisterous%20rhetoric%20of%20supremacy%E2%80%9D%2C%20leaving%20no%20doubt%20whom%20he%20considered%20the%20enemy.%20And%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20reiterated%20the%20majoritarian%20trope%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20simple%20truth%20is%20this%3A%20Hindustan%20(the%20land%20of%20the%20Hindus)%20should%20remain%20Hindustan%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20unspoken%20implication%20being%20that%20minorities%20live%20here%20on%20sufferance.%20There%20was%20no%20public%20outrage%20as%20he%20was%20merely%20articulating%20this%20majoritarian%20government%E2%80%99s%20creed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20undeniable%20that%20in%20the%20two%20largest%20democracies%2C%20the%20invasion%20of%20neo-Nazis%2C%20supremacists%20and%20extreme%20right-wing%20nationalists%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20political%20and%20cultural%20discourse%20has%20coincided%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20Modi%20and%20Trump.%20There%20is%20an%20eerie%20similarity%20in%20the%20concepts%20deployed%20by%20their%20advocates%20to%20foment%20fear%20and%20loathing%20among%20their%20constituents.%20The%20toxic%20disinformation%20regarding%20an%20embattled%20white%20majority%20population%20being%20overwhelmed%20by%20immigrants%20is%20twinned%20with%20the%20criminal%20predisposition%20of%20immigrants.%20This%20is%20matched%20by%20the%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20propaganda%20of%20disproportionate%20increase%20in%20the%20Muslim%20population%2C%20their%20enticement%20of%20Hindu%20women%20through%20love%20jihad%2C%20their%20food%20jihad%20and%20the%20enduring%20theme%20of%20their%20disloyalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20whereas%20the%20white%20supremacists%E2%80%99%20strategy%20of%20expanding%20their%20base%20is%20limited%20to%20tapping%20potential%20fellow-travellers%20and%20sneaking%20into%20mainstream%20media%20and%20political%20debate%2C%20the%20majoritarian%20nationalism%20in%20our%20midst%20that%20is%20on%20a%20crusade%20against%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%20and%20anything%20or%20anybody%20perceived%20as%20inimical%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20project%2C%20has%20now%20spread%20its%20tentacles%20everywhere.%20With%20its%20arsenal%20of%20zealous%20mobs%2C%20Goebbelsian%20propaganda%2C%20media%20lapdogs%2C%20infiltrated%20institutions%2C%20inexhaustible%20funds%20et%20al.%2C%20it%20has%20captured%20the%20social%20space.%20Manipur%20and%20Nuh%20are%20a%20foretaste%20of%20things%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20staring%20into%20the%20abyss!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20Views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693280234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F25184020%2FIMG_0015.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-manipur-nuh-ethnic-violence-partition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%20arsenal%20of%20zealous%20mobs%2C%20Goebbelsian%20propaganda%2C%20media%20lapdogs%2C%20infiltrated%20institutions%2C%20inexhaustible%20funds%20et%20al.%2C%20it%20has%20captured%20the%20social%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-manipur-nuh-ethnic-violence-partition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guatemala%20body%20ratifies%20presidential%20vote%20result%20amid%20new%20bid%20to%20thwart%20victor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693279889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103155533%2Cimgsize-22600.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fguatemala-body-ratifies-presidential-vote-result-amid-new-bid-to-thwart-victor%2Farticleshow%2F103155092.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%2