nday%20afternoon%20only%20to%20turn%20out%20as%20a%20high%20drama%20staged%20by%20the%20trio%20to%20bunk%20classes%20for%20the%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22K%20SAROJKUMAR%20SARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fimphal%2F3-schoolgirls-stage-kidnap-drama-to-bunk-classes-in-bishnupur-dist%2Farticleshow%2F103154994.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20BRICS%20Expansion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29085027%2FF4StBG3WEAAghXF.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20of%20BRICS%20to%20include%20four%20West%20Asian%20nations%20along%20with%20two%20other%20influential%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20one%20African%20and%20the%20other%20South%20American%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20a%20head%20turner%2C%20given%20the%20current%20geopolitical%20fluidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20are%20expected%20to%20accept%20the%20invitation%20to%20join%20though%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20injected%20a%20note%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20process%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cconsider%E2%80%9D%20the%20invitation%20and%20make%20%E2%80%9Can%20appropriate%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20takeaways%20from%20the%20summit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisillusionment%20with%20the%20US%2FWest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20membership%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Iran%2C%20UAE%20and%20Egypt%20%E2%80%93%20Ethiopia%20and%20Argentina%20are%20the%20two%20other%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20in%20BRICS%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20January%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enthusiasm%20for%20BRICS%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region%20signals%20that%20it%20no%20longer%20sees%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20world%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20weakening%20US%20influence%20in%20the%20region%20became%20apparent%20with%20the%20China-brokered%20Saudi-Iran%20peace%20deal%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Barring%20Iran%2C%20each%20of%20these%20nations%20has%20been%20a%20close%20US%20ally%20until%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20US%20may%20have%20begun%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%20During%20the%20Arab%20Spring%2C%20the%20Obama%20administration%E2%80%99s%20abandonment%20of%20close%20ally%20Hosni%20Mubarak%20was%20a%20rude%20awakening%20for%20other%20long%20standing%20American%20friends%20and%20partners%20from%20Saudi%20to%20Bahrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20George%20Bush%E2%80%99s%202003%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%20and%20the%20overthrow%20of%20Saddam%20Hussein%E2%80%99s%20Baath%20regime%20strengthened%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20clout%20in%20the%20Shia-majority%20country%20and%20in%20the%20region.%20Eight%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Saudis%20and%20the%20Gulf%20Co-operation%20Council%E2%80%99s%20Persian%20Shield%20army%20had%20to%20rush%20to%20the%20rescue%20of%20the%20Sunni%20rulers%20of%20Shia-majority%20Bahrain%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20a%20nascent%20%E2%80%9CArab%20Spring%E2%80%9D%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Obama%20administration%E2%80%99s%20pivot%20to%20Asia%2C%20and%20engagement%20with%20Iran%20for%20a%20nuclear%20deal%20convinced%20Riyadh%20that%20the%20US%20focus%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20Asia-Pacific.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20tough%20talk%20against%20Iran%20rekindled%20Saudi%20hope%20in%20its%20benefactor%2C%20only%20for%20it%20to%20shatter%20when%20Washington%20did%20nothing%20to%20help%20as%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20rebels%20struck%20two%20of%20its%20refineries%20halting%20production%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20the%20region.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20UAE%20%5Bjoining%20BRICS%5D%20is%20symbolic%20of%20the%20disenchantment%20of%20the%20West%20Asian%20countries%20with%20the%20US%20as%20a%20security%20provider%20in%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Talmiz%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Oman%20and%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20plus%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20younger%20leadership%2C%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20in%20Saudi%2C%20and%20Mohammed%20bin%20Zayed%20in%20UAE%2C%20have%20marked%20what%20Ahmed%20called%20%E2%80%9Ca%20coming%20of%20age%20moment%20for%20these%20two%20countries%2C%20a%20return%20of%20national%20self-confidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20major%20oil%20producing%20countries%20had%20decided%20to%20find%20their%20own%20place%20in%20the%20world%20in%20pursuit%20of%20their%20own%20interests%2C%20said%20Ahmed.%20Riyadh%20has%20more%20strategic%20ambitions%20than%20the%20UAE%20and%20wants%20to%20wield%20more%20influence%20on%20its%20own%2C%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20while%20the%20UAE%20is%20focussed%20on%20pushing%20its%20commercial%20interests.%20Countries%20in%20West%20Asia%20%E2%80%9Cwant%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20East%20Asian%20success%20story%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20former%20ambassador%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-brics-22-countries-expansion-stakes%5C%22%3EAs%20BRICS%20Evolves%20Criteria%20for%20Expansion%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20India%20Thinks%20of%20the%2022%20Countries%20That%20Want%20to%20Join%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20less%20isolated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20membership%20of%20BRICS%20gives%20Iran%20an%20opportunity%20to%20signal%20that%20the%20US%20attempt%20to%20isolate%20it%20has%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20forged%20close%20ties%20with%20China%20(the%20two%20sides%20have%20reportedly%20signed%20a%20%E2%80%9C25-year%20co-operation%20programme%E2%80%9D)%20and%20Russia.%20With%20Chinese%20mediation%2C%20Iran%20signed%20a%20peace%20agreement%20with%20Saudi.%20The%20deal%20has%20stopped%20the%20fighting%20in%20Yemen%2C%20though%20the%20conflict%20in%20that%20country%20still%20awaits%20resolution.%20Iran%20has%20supplied%20Russia%20with%20several%20hundred%20attack%20and%20surveillance%20drones%20for%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20By%20mid-2023%2C%20the%20drones%20were%20being%20manufactured%20in%20Russia%20with%20Iranian%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%2C%20an%20anti-west%20hardliner%2C%20told%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20that%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20grouping%20would%20bring%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20benefits%E2%80%9D.%20Under%20UN%20sanctions%20for%20much%20of%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Iran%20has%20been%20an%20early%20votary%20of%20%E2%80%9Cde-dollarisation%E2%80%9D%20or%20trade%20in%20local%20currencies.%20On%20returning%20to%20Tehran%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al-monitor.com%2Foriginals%2F2023%2F08%2Fraisi-pushes-anti-us-agenda-brics-iran-celebrates-ascension%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Islamic%2520Republic%2520hopes%2520that%2Cinfluence%2520in%2520the%2520global%2520sphere.%26amp%3Btext%3DIran%2527s%2520President%2520Ebrahim%2520Raisi%2520told%2Cdollar%2520in%2520their%2520economic%2520dealings%5C%22%3ERaisi%20told%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20BRICS%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20random%20occurrence%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Ca%20policy%20pursued%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20well-oiled%20BRICS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grouping%20now%20has%20five%20of%20the%20top%2010%20oil%20producing%20countries%2C%20adding%20to%20its%20financial%20and%20economic%20heft.%20Saudi%20and%20founding%20members%20Russia%20and%20Brazil%20are%20respectively%20the%20second%2C%20third%20and%20eighth%20biggest%20oil%20producing%20countries%20(the%20US%20tops%20the%20list)%2C%20while%20UAE%20and%20Iran%20are%20ranked%20seventh%20and%20ninth%20respectively.%20The%20three%20West%20Asian%20countries%20are%20key%20members%20of%20OPEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20this%20will%20play%20out%20for%20oil%20production%20and%20prices%20versus%20demand%20is%20to%20be%20seen.%20What%20is%20apparent%20since%20last%20year%20is%20that%20Saudi%20has%20ignored%20repeated%20US%20calls%20not%20to%20cut%20production%20as%20it%20would%20blunt%20the%20impact%20of%20sanctions%20on%20Moscow.%20Instead%2C%20Saudi%20has%20cooperated%20with%20Russia%20in%20OPEC%2B%20to%20do%20exactly%20this%20in%20order%20to%20prop%20up%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20reached%20yet%20another%20agreement%20to%20deepen%20production%20cuts%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20increase%20prices%2C%20which%20have%20remained%20low%20due%20to%20sluggish%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Asian%20presence%20in%20BRICS%20puts%20the%20OPEC%20big%20shots%20in%20the%20same%20room%20as%20big%20oil%20consumers.%20Despite%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20determined%20push%20to%20replace%20fossil%20fuels%20with%20renewables%2C%20accelerated%20by%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20despite%20the%20slowing%20down%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy%2C%20China%20along%20with%20India%20will%20remain%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20oil%20consumers%20for%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20expected%20that%20Saudi%20will%20seek%20more%20clout%20within%20the%20grouping%20with%20investment%20in%20the%20BRICS%20bank%2C%20called%20the%20National%20Development%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBRICS%20and%20blocs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20BRICS%20emphasise%20that%20it%20is%20not%20an%20anti-Western%20bloc%2C%20and%20speak%20about%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20autonomy%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20multipolarity%2C%20and%20having%20their%20voice%20heard%20in%20the%20global%20arena.%20This%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20main%20attraction%20for%20the%20long%20waiting%20list%20for%20joining%20it%2C%20at%20last%20count%2040%20countries.%20Access%20to%20China%20is%20always%20good%20leverage%20in%20negotiations%20with%20the%20West.%C2%A0%20Interestingly%20though%2C%20the%20summit%20declaration%20affirmed%20the%20importance%20of%20US-Iran%20efforts%20to%20restore%20the%202015%20nuclear%20deal%20(or%20Joint%20Comprehensive%20Plan%20of%20Action)%20%E2%80%9Cand%20hope%20for%20relevant%20parties%20to%20restore%20the%20full%20and%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20JCPOA%20at%20an%20early%20date%E2%80%9D%2C%20appearing%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20President%20Raisi%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20the%20US%20had%20nothing%20more%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20also%20that%20two%20powerful%20BRICS%20members%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20are%20locked%20in%20adversarial%20relations%20with%20the%20US.%20And%20the%20queue%20to%20join%20the%20grouping%20is%20a%20validation%20that%20they%20still%20carry%20enough%20influence%20in%20the%20world%20for%20these%20countries%20to%20want%20to%20associate%20with%20them.%20Inevitably%2C%20BRICS%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20anti-US%2Fanti-west%20bloc%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20China%20sees%20the%20Quad%20as%20a%20US-led%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20circle%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20Cold%20war-style%20camps%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9CAsian%20NATO%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20excellent%20ties%20with%20each%20of%20the%20BRICS%20members%2C%20including%20the%20new%20ones%2C%20the%20technology%20boost%20of%20Chandrayaan%20-3%E2%80%99s%20moon%20landing%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20demography%20and%20its%20growing%20economy%2C%20all%20give%20it%20influence%20in%20the%20group%20potentially%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20turning%20into%20an%20anti-West%20bloc.%20But%20as%20the%20most%20powerful%20country%20in%20BRICS%2C%20China%20dominates%20the%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20membership%20of%20BRICS%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20oddity%20for%20a%20country%20that%20is%20in%20a%20deep%20and%20nationally%20celebrated%20embrace%20with%20the%20US.%20But%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20aspiration%20to%20be%20accepted%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CGlobal%20South%E2%80%9D%20and%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20a%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20are%20clearly%20better%20served%20by%20multilateralism%20of%20the%20BRICS%20kind%2C%20even%20if%20China%20is%20the%20dominant%20player.%20The%20summit%20declaration%20contains%20an%20unequivocal%20paragraph%20on%20supporting%20the%20claims%20of%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20Brazil%20for%20%E2%80%9Ca%20greater%20role%20in%20international%20affairs%2C%20in%20particular%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20including%20its%20Security%20Council%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20used%20BRICS%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Shanghai%20Co-operation%20Organisation%20to%20keep%20lines%20open%20to%20Beijing%20for%20a%20diplomatic%20resolution%20of%20the%20LAC%20dispute%2C%20however%20dim%20the%20chances%20look%20for%20a%20return%20to%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20April%202020.%20The%20Modi-Xi%20meeting%20on%20the%20summit%E2%80%99s%20sidelines%20had%20no%20breakthroughs%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManaging%20differences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20commentary%20on%20BRICS%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20grouping%20that%20lacks%20inner%20cohesion%2C%20and%20note%20that%20it%20will%20remain%20hobbled%20by%20adversarial%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20The%20same%20could%20be%20said%20of%20G20%20with%20Russia%20and%20China%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20Western%20members%20of%20the%20grouping.%20At%20the%20recent%20summit%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20BRICS%20was%20able%20to%20manage%20its%20differences%20to%20agree%20on%20admitting%20six%20new%20members.%20It%20also%20put%20out%20a%20communique%20acceptable%20to%20all%20including%20India%2C%20that%20the%20more%20powerful%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccohesive%E2%80%9D%20G20%20may%20yet%20fail%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%20the%20BRICS%20document%20skipped%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20entirely%2C%20and%20instead%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cconcern%20at%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20conflicts%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20formulation%20that%20would%20not%20pass%20muster%20in%20most%20other%20multilateral%20fora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Johannesburg%20Declaration%20does%20refer%20to%20G%2020%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpremier%20multilateral%20forum%20in%20the%20field%20of%20international%20economic%20and%20financial%20cooperation%20that%20comprises%20both%20developed%20and%20emerging%20markets%20and%20developing%20countries%20where%20major%20economies%20jointly%20seek%20solutions%20to%20global%20challenges%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20good%20augury%20for%20India%2C%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20said%20it%20looked%20forward%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20successful%20hosting%20of%20the%2018th%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20under%20the%20Indian%20G20%20Presidency%E2%80%9D%20boosting%20hopes%20that%20there%20might%20be%20consensus%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Declaration%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-tooltip%3D%5C%22Show%20trimmed%20content%5C%22%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENirupama%20Subramanian%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693279342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29085027%2FF4StBG3WEAAghXF.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbrics-expansion-saudi-arabia-oil-iran%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20enthusiasm%20for%20BRICS%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region%20signals%20that%20it%20no%20longer%20sees%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20world%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20United%20States.%22%2