l%20requirement%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20an%20assembly%20session%20every%20six%20months%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20direct%20rule%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20that%20particular%20state.%20The%20last%20session%20in%20Manipur%20was%20held%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March%2C%20meaning%20that%20by%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September%2C%20the%20governor%20has%20to%20call%20the%20next%20session%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20governor%20Uikey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-special-session-anusuiya-uikey-biren%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20heed%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20formal%20request%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hold%20the%20session%20initially%2C%20she%20eventually%20did%2C%20leaving%20one%20to%20only%20conclude%20that%20she%20must%20have%20done%20so%20at%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Union%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20BJP-ruled%20state%20is%20not%20seen%20hurtling%20towards%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20constitutional%20aberration%20of%20holding%20a%20single%20sitting%20of%20a%20regular%20assembly%20session%20in%20Manipur%20is%2C%20however%2C%20only%20a%20continuation%20of%20what%20governors%20appointed%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20are%20increasingly%20seen%20to%20be%20doing%20in%20several%20states%20%E2%80%93%20going%20against%20the%20norm.%20The%20phenomenon%20is%20noticed%20both%20in%20BJP%20and%20opposition-ruled%20states.%20If%20we%20focus%20on%20the%20details%2C%20each%20instance%20comes%20across%20more%20as%20an%20act%20by%20a%20political%20appointee%20than%20intended%20to%20protect%20the%20constitution%20which%20the%20governors%20are%20expected%20to%20safeguard%20in%20each%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPunjab%20assembly%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20Punjab.%20Governor%20Banwarilal%20Purohit%20is%20taking%20on%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Punjab%2C%20an%20opposition-ruled%20state%2C%20based%20on%20his%20allegation%20that%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20government%20is%20facilitating%20the%20drug%20menace%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Feditorials%2Frespect-the-constitution-101693188988916.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dhurt%2520India%2527s%2520democracy.-%2CArticle%2520356%2520should%2520only%2520be%2520reserved%2520as%2520a%2520last%2520resort%2Cmore%2520respectful%2520of%2520other%2520authorities%5C%22%3Egovernor%20is%20threatening%20to%20recommend%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20the%20the%20chief%20minister%20not%20responding%20on%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20interesting%20is%20this%20threat%20of%20the%20governor%20to%20recommend%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20Punjab%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Union%20has%20doggedly%20refused%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Manipur%20even%20after%20at%20least%20150%20people%20have%20lost%20lives%20in%20an%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20leaving%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20in%20relief%20camps%20since%20May%20and%20voices%20from%20within%20both%20Kukis%20and%20Meiteis%20demanding%20the%20accountability%20of%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20with%20some%20even%20demanding%20his%20resignation%20for%20failing%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%20Importantly%2C%20thousands%20of%20arms%20were%20looted%20from%20police%20stations%20to%20kill%20innocent%20people.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20also%20the%20state%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Punjab%20governor%E2%80%99s%20threat%20particularly%20strikes%20as%20odd%20when%20you%20also%20take%20into%20cognisance%20that%20an%20affidavit%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20in%202020%20by%20a%20state%20police%20officer%20handling%20the%20anti-drug%20drive%20stating%20that%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20had%20categorically%20asked%20her%20to%20go%20slow%20in%20some%20drug-related%20cases.%20No%20action%20was%20seen%20taken%20on%20that%20front%20either%20by%20the%20then%20state%20governor%20nor%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETamil%20Nadu%20assembly%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELook%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20After%20a%20face-off%20with%20the%20NSCN%20(Isak-Muivah)%20leaders%2C%20and%20several%20minor%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20state%20government%20led%20by%20BJP-ally%20National%20Democratic%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(NDPP)%2C%20the%20Centre%20removed%20Nagaland%20governor%20R.N.%20Ravi%20from%20his%20position%20and%20also%20as%20its%20interlocutor%20for%20the%20Indo-Naga%20peace%20talks%20in%202021.%20It%20also%20transferred%20him%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Raj%20Bhavan%20from%20the%20Kohima%20Raj%20Bhavan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERavi%2C%20as%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%2C%20has%20since%20been%20acting%20more%20like%20a%20political%20appointee%20than%20going%20by%20the%20constitutional%20rulebook.%20One%20such%20aberration%20was%20regularly%20blocking%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20assembly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20he%20claimed%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20no%20bills%20were%20pending%20before%20him%20unlike%20what%20was%20claimed%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Fthirteen-bills-pending-before-tn-governor-despite-his-earlier-claims%2Famp%5C%22%3Ean%20RTI%20reply%20recently%20revealed%20as%20many%20as%2013%20bills%20have%20been%20pending%20before%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20January%2C%20Ravi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-governor-skips-reference-to-dravidian-leaders-dravidian-model-of-government-in-his-assembly-address%2Farticle66355909.ece%3F_gl%3D1*42b503*_ga*VHFia0huSmJndExEMm1ydU5vR2JyZjFqS0dqRkRnR3NRZGd6RmpOZnc4VDBWM1hRWkFJMVRKTEZaMHBVbC13Ng%5C%22%3Ehit%20the%20headlines%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%20to%20refuse%20to%20read%20a%20portion%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20text%20of%20his%20customary%20address%20to%20the%20assembly%20put%20together%20by%20the%20DMK%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20an%20aberration%20that%20took%20place%20also%20in%20the%20Kerala%20assembly%20in%202018%2C%20carried%20out%20by%20another%20Modi%20government%20appointed%20governor%20in%20the%20Left-ruled%20Kerala.%20In%20that%20southern%20state%20too%2C%20the%20current%20governor%20Arif%20Mohammad%20Khan%20has%20been%20following%20the%20same%20script%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkerala%2Fkerala-governor-arif-mohammed-khan-press-conference-in-thiruvananthapuram-on-september-19-2022%2Farticle65909682.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3Econtinuously%20taking%20on%20the%20opposition-ruled%20state%20government%20on%20some%20trivial%20matter%20or%20the%20other%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thereby%20behaving%20more%20like%20a%20political%20appointee%20than%20a%20constitutional%20head%20of%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%20seemed%20to%20have%20crossed%20the%20line%20even%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%E2%80%99%20estimates%20recently%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20dismiss%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20of%20the%20Stalin%20government.%20With%20the%20state%20government%20threatening%20to%20go%20to%20the%20court%20for%20violation%20of%20a%20constitutional%20norm%2C%20Ravi%20had%20to%20back%20off%20at%20the%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20intervention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERajasthan%20assembly%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20governor%20has%20called%20the%20assembly%20session%20without%20following%20the%20usual%20practice%20of%20granting%20at%20least%20a%2015-day%20notice%20to%20the%20legislators%20before%20announcing%20commencement%20of%20a%20session%2C%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20yet%20another%20Modi%20government-appointed%20governor%2C%20Kalraj%20Mishra%2C%20had%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20request%20from%20the%20Congress-run%20state%20government%20to%20hold%20a%20session%20because%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20the%20MLAs%20a%2021-day%20notice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20that%20session%20in%202020%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20facing%20a%20power%20tussle%20within%20his%20party%2C%20with%20the%20rebel%20faction%20comprising%2019%20MLAs%20having%20approached%20the%20governor%20to%20not%20hold%20the%20session.%20Three%20times%2C%20the%20state%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20to%20hold%20an%20assembly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-governor-accepts-4th-gehlot-proposal-approves-assembly-session-from-august-14%2Fstory-Vr7F8MuduFNbkhTDa9yiFI_amp.html%5C%22%3Esession%20to%20prove%20his%20majority%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20was%20rejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20the%20pandemic%2C%20something%20political%20observers%20had%20then%20viewed%20as%20the%20governor%20acting%20to%20favour%20the%20Congress%20rebels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArunachal%20Pradesh%20assembly%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20holding%20assembly%20sessions%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20constitutional%20aberrations%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20in%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20then%20governor%20J.K.%20Rajkhowa%2C%2033%20Congress%20rebel%20legislators%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fin-arunachal-testing-the-frontiers-of-political-propriety%2Famp%5C%22%3Emet%20at%20a%20community%20hall%20in%20Naharlagun%20to%20topple%20the%20Congress%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20ultimately%20clear%20the%20passage%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20BJP%20government%20in%20that%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20delivered%20a%20judgement%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20beleaguered%20Congress%20government%20but%20by%20then%2C%20the%20country%20had%20already%20registered%20a%20constitutional%20aberration%20that%2C%20on%20looking%20back%20now%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20ushered%20many%20more%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693278050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21123029%2F368240334_852277936254542_98828167759017360_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-monsoon-session-anusuiya-uikey%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fact%20that%20the%20session%20will%20wrap%20up%20today%20itself%20is%20indication%20that%20the%20BJP%20governments%20at%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20are%20keen%20to%20project%20that%20things%20are%20'functional'%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20this%20decision%20rests%20on%20a%20constitutional%20aberration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-monsoon-session-anusuiya-uikey%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea's%20Kim%20calls%20for%20readiness%20to%20smash%20US-led%20invasion%20plot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693277538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103152779%2Cimgsize-852962.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnorth-koreas-kim-calls-for-readiness-to-smash-us-