235703387%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Nuh%20Violence%2C%20Farmers%20and%20Khap%20Panchayats%20in%20Mewat%20Stand%20Up%20Against%20Hate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11145030%2Fimg-20230811-wa0017.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThousands%20of%20farmers%20converged%20at%20a%20Mahapanchayat%20held%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Alwar%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2026%2C%20vowing%20to%20counter%20the%20politics%20of%20hatred%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20recent%20violence%20that%20rocked%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20July%2031%20when%20Nuh%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20and%20adjoining%20areas%20of%20Haryana%20witnessed%20anti-Muslim%20violence%20during%20a%20rally%20taken%20out%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20groups%20have%20held%20three%20major%20meetings%20in%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20and%20Mewat%20to%20counter%20the%20communal%20build-up%20in%20the%20state.%20Besides%2C%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20local%20Khap%20panchayat%20meetings%20have%20been%20held%20across%20the%20Mewat%20region%2C%20which%20spans%20both%20Haryana%20and%20neighbouring%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20meeting%20on%20August%209%20at%20a%20grain%20market%20in%20Hisar%E2%80%99s%20Bass%20village%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20convened%20to%20discuss%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%2C%20was%20renamed%20%3Cspan%3EBhaichara%20Sammelan%20(a%20meeting%20to%20spread%20brotherhood)%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20Nuh%20and%20Gurugram%20violence%20and%20subsequent%20hate%20speeches%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20calling%20for%20the%20boycott%20of%20Muslims.%20Since%20farmers%E2%80%99%20pushback%20against%20the%20hate%2C%20calls%20for%20such%20a%20boycott%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20have%20largely%20stopped%20from%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20warning%20that%20further%20bloodshed%20in%20Haryana%20has%20been%20averted%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EShamsher%20Singh%20More%2C%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leader%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMewatis%20are%20our%20brothers.%20They%20stood%20with%20us%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20organised%20%3Cem%3Elangars%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%20supporters%20attacked%20and%20defamed%20us%2C%20by%20calling%20us%20terrorists.%20We%20are%20not%20returning%20any%20favour%20but%20we%20are%20standing%20with%20our%20brothers%20against%20miscreants%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20disharmony%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20goes%20on%20to%20add%20that%20people%20have%20%E2%80%9Cunited%20to%20stop%20polarisation%E2%80%9D%20before%20the%20upcoming%20state%20and%20parliamentary%20elections.%20It%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20besides%20farmers%2C%20the%20long-drawn%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20protest%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20communal%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20addition%20to%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20demand%20for%20action%20against%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20focus%20of%20the%20state%20should%20be%20on%20education%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20instead%20of%20religious%20disputes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leader%20Suresh%20Kouth%2C%20who%20emerged%20as%20a%20prominent%20face%20during%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20three%20contentious%20farm%20laws%2C%20said%20such%20meetings%20are%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20want%20to%20save%20our%20state.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20disharmony%20in%20Haryana.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20riots%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kouth%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20questioning%20inaction%20against%20hate-mongers%20such%20as%20Monu%20Manesar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20murdering%20two%20Muslim%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFarmers%20becoming%20overtly%20religious%20harms%20the%20interests%20of%20people%20at%20large%20and%20disturbs%20communal%20harmony%2C%20said%20another%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leader%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EChoudhary%20Chotu%20Ram.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Hindus%2C%20we%20are%20more%20in%20number%20and%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20protect%20those%20who%20are%20fewer%20in%20numbers%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20attack.%20Before%20anyone%20points%20a%20finger%20at%20them%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20face%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20denied%20permission%20to%20Hindutva%20groups%20to%20hold%20another%20%E2%80%98Shobha%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20in%20Nuh%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2028%20%E2%80%93%20akin%20to%20the%20one%20held%20on%20July%2031%20which%20saw%20widespread%20violence.%20Although%20Hindutva%20groups%20vowed%20to%20take%20out%20a%20rally%20on%20Monday%20despite%20being%20denied%20permission%2C%20police%20barred%20them%20from%20doing%20so.%20Instead%2C%20the%20police%20allowed%20groups%20of%2010-20%20people%20to%20perform%20Jalabhishek%20at%20different%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20posse%20of%20policemen%20was%20deployed%20in%20Nuh%20and%20Gurugram%20on%20Monday%20anticipating%20violence.%20Farmers%20had%20earlier%20warned%20of%20a%20tractor%20rally%20if%20the%20Haryana%20government%20were%20to%20permit%20any%20rally%20by%20Hindutva%20groups.%20%3Cspan%3EThey%20have%20been%20blaming%20the%20BJP%20governments%20in%20Haryana%20and%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20giving%20patronage%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20groups%20to%20stoke%20religious%20hatred%20in%20Mewat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20%E2%80%93%20who%20has%20been%20covering%20farmers%E2%80%99%20meetings%20and%20Khap%20panchayats%20closely%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20it%20is%20due%20to%20such%20coming%20together%20of%20forces%20against%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20not%20become%20worse%20in%20the%20Mewat%20region.%20He%20said%20since%20Khaps%20dominate%20politics%20in%20Haryana%2C%20their%20influence%20is%20seen%20in%20averting%20any%20further%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhupinder%20Chaudhary%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20spokesperson%20who%20attended%20some%20of%20these%20meetings%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20what%20matters%20more%20than%20the%20larger%20political%20impact%20of%20these%20meetings%20is%20the%20message%20of%20solidarity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20dominant%20community%20rejects%20hate%20politics%2C%20it%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20all%20other%20communities.%20To%20the%20Muslims%2C%20the%20message%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20alone%20and%20everybody%20is%20not%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20This%20reassurance%20is%20important.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20partner%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20had%20said%20that%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh%20could%20have%20been%20averted%20had%20the%20organisers%20shared%20correct%20information%20with%20the%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693272637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11145030%2Fimg-20230811-wa0017.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fafter-nuh-violence-farmers-and-khap-panchayats-in-mewat-stand-up-against-hate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20July%2031%2C%20farmers%20have%20held%20three%20major%20meetings%20in%20the%20region%20to%20counter%20the%20communal%20build-up%20in%20Haryana.