%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20final.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A315%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluis-rubiales-spanish-football-federation-calls-for-president-to-resign-over-world-cup-kiss-12949905%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fluis-rubiales-spanish-football-federation-calls-for-president-to-resign-over-world-cup-kiss-12949905%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fluis-rubiales-spanish-football-federation-calls-for-president-to-resign-over-world-cup-kiss-12949905%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Govt%20Defensive%20Over%20Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%2C%20Changes%20Affidavit%20in%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20filed%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20late%20on%20Monday%20evening%20noting%20that%20a%20certain%20paragraph%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98previous%E2%80%99%20affidavit%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinadvertently%20crept%20in%E2%80%9D.%20The%20paragraph%20in%20question%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20body%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20otherwise%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20affidavit%20comes%20following%20criticism%20from%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal.%20They%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20neither%20wants%20to%20conduct%20a%20census%20nationally%20nor%20does%20it%20want%20Bihar%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Union%20government%20dropping%20para%205%20from%20the%20previous%20affidavit%20and%20filing%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%2C%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20view%20on%20the%20matter%20remains%20the%20same.%20The%20new%20affidavit%20says%20that%20a%20census%20is%20a%20statutory%20process%20governed%20by%20the%20Census%20Act%20of%201948%2C%20which%20was%20enacted%20in%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20powers%20under%20Entry%2069%20of%20List%20I%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%99s%20Seventh%20Schedule%20and%20that%20the%20said%20Act%20empowers%20only%20the%20Central%20Government%20to%20conduct%20the%20Census%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbihar-caste-survey-case-state-govt-census-centre-tells-supreme-court-236420%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%2C%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20was%20eager%20to%20convey%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20in%20any%20way%20obstructing%20the%20Bihar%20census%2C%20when%20he%20told%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20was%20neither%20opposing%20nor%20supporting%20the%20litigation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20move%20came%20shortly%20after%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20had%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20no%20knowledge.%20They%20only%20know%20how%20to%20lie%20and%20suppress%20the%20truth.%20They%20have%20opposed%20it%20even%20in%20the%20affidavit%E2%80%A6%20It%20has%20been%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20it%20and%20is%20opposing%20it.%20If%20they%20support%20it%2C%20then%20they%20should%20conduct%20it%20(caste%20census)%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fani%2Fstatus%2F1696182944719925418%3Fs%3D46%26t%3D1vwSP919utJCl83SiqVxmg%5C%22%3Ehe%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20RJD%20patriarch%20and%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20had%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20the%20issue.%20He%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20a%20hostile%20attitude%20towards%20the%20caste%20survey%20conducted%20in%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20of%20this%20country%20seems%20distressed%20with%20castes.%20He%20keeps%20mentioning%20%E2%80%98Jati%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20speeches%2C%20perhaps%20he%20thinks%20this%20social%20reality%20will%20not%20let%20him%20enjoy%20peace.%20He%20is%20right%20if%20he%20thinks%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Faug%2F26%2Fmodi-govt-hostile-towards-caste-survey-in-bihar-lalu-prasad-2608977.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20say%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20followed%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20said%20they%20are%20for%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20on%20the%20backfoot%20and%20anxious%20to%20evade%20the%20subject.%20It%20has%20problems%20with%20agreeing%20to%20do%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20as%20it%20is%20fundamentally%20at%20odds%20with%20its%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20seeking%20%E2%80%98vertical%20integration%E2%80%99%20of%20all%20castes%20under%20a%20Hindutva%20umbrella%20and%20also%20not%20suitable%20for%20it%20politically.%20It%20feels%20such%20a%20survey%20will%20only%20benefit%20the%20Opposition%20speaking%20of%20empowerment%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%20is%20complete%2C%20similar%20surveys%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20launched%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20stating%20that%20detailed%20information%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20state%20would%20help%20create%20better%20government%20policy%20to%20aid%20disadvantaged%20groups.%20The%20entire%20exercise%20was%20sup