0Technologies%2C%20and%20Acuity%20Knowledge%20Partners%20who%20offer%20resources%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20funding%20to%20support%20the%20sustainability%20of%20our%20initiative%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%981%20Million%20by%202025%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20says%20that%20every%20year%2C%20they%20conduct%20an%20annual%20survey%20to%20understand%20the%20experience%20of%20children%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F105260%2Findia-literacy-project-interactive-learning-rural-government-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1uEv8ngaoPY4ZrB19oQVB6pRnFMv-86TuFXHxKt9R9HY%2Fedit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E95.2%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20children%20are%20enjoying%20the%20digital%20learning%20experience%20as%20compared%20to%20before%20our%20intervention%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20is%20planning%20to%20reach%20out%20to%201%20million%20students%20by%202025.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F