f%20children%20are%20taught%20how%20to%20read%20a%20food%20label%20and%20understand%20the%20consequences%2C%20it%20will%20bring%20about%20a%20massive%20change.%20Companies%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20market%20themselves%20honestly%2C%20and%20this%20will%20change%20the%20game.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20and%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Freports%2Fstate-of-worlds-children-2019%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNICEF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692353848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FRevant-1692350285.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327558%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Revant%20Himatsingka%2C%20aka%20foodpharmer%20on%20Instagram%2C%20terms%20reading%20food%20labels%20the%20most%20important%20life%20skill.%20His%20aim%20is%20to%20expose%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20marketing%E2%80%9D%20by%20FMCGs%20and%20educate%20people%20on%20what%20they%20are%20truly%20consuming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%E2%80%99s%20Low-Cost%20Model%20Helps%208000%20Farmers%20Cut%2099%25%20Water%20Use%2C%20Harvest%20500%20KG%20Fodder%2FDay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20as%20a%20sales%20engineer%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Ashwin%20Sawant%20met%20a%20client%20who%20was%20cultivating%20green%20fodder%20hydroponically%20for%20his%20large%20livestock%2C%20consisting%20of%20over%202%2C000%20animals.%20This%20farm%20left%20such%20an%20impre